{"tid":2488044,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"拋雜物入火堆助燃　女咖啡師縱火暴動罪成囚4年半","createTime":"2021-04-14T03:32:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T03:40:34.000Z","uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7ea3ee7d7b58b018a81bca92155c40190b6a79e8","tid":2488044,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T03:32:05.000Z","msg":"前年9月有示威者在旺角警署外聚集，期間有人佔據太子道西行車線，並點燃雜物。一名27歲女咖啡師將雜物丟入火堆助燃，早前被裁定兩項縱火及一項暴動罪成，早上在區域法院被判入獄4年半。<br />\n<br />\n被告被控於前年9月22日在旺角太子道西西行及彌敦道交界，兩度縱火及參與暴動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1585705-20210414.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1585705-20210414.htm&d=t2%2FAN0mLur8%2Bj%2B1TvbkzvgKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=1a780d62\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1585705-20210414.htm&h=ad5aeeb3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1585705-20210414.htm</a>"},{"pid":"131336d285c21d1a84b128730c4094c3729157cb","tid":2488044,"uid":227217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T03:40:34.000Z","msg":"推"}]}